{"tid":2268666,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周四到期社交距離措施維持不變　教育局下周起為中小學幼稚園教職員驗病毒","createTime":"2020-11-03T03:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T04:59:37.000Z","uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"18ed8143620044e5deae5cf3d821c01f91740e8f","tid":2268666,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:35:02.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥今早（3日）見記者宣布，因應最新新型冠狀病毒疫情，周四（5日）到期的社交距離措施會維持不變，為期一周，稍後食物及衛生局會發出相關指引。<span class=\"red\"><strong>她又表示，教育局由下周起，會為幼稚園、中小學及特殊學校教職員分批進行新冠病毒檢測。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又表示，醫管局會加強向有輕微病徵者提供病毒檢測的服務，目前有派發樣本瓶的46間普通科門診診所，本周起周六亦會派樣本瓶，其中8間在周日及公眾假期都會派樽，3間診所會加設樣本瓶自動派發機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201103/s00001/1604368596426/%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-%e5%91%a8%e5%9b%9b%e5%88%b0%e6%9c%9f%e7%a4%be%e4%ba%a4%e8%b7%9d%e9%9b%a2%e6%8e%aa%e6%96%bd%e7%b6%ad%e6%8c%81%e4%b8%8d%e8%ae%8a-%e6%95%99%e8%82%b2%e5%b1%80%e4%b8%8b%e5%91%a8%e8%b5%b7%e7%82%ba%e4%b8%ad%e5%b0%8f%e5%ad%b8%e5%b9%bc%e7%a8%9a%e5%9c%92%e6%95%99%e8%81%b7%e5%93%a1%e9%a9%97%e7%97%85%e6%af%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201103%2Fs00001%2F1604368596426%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e5%2591%25a8%25e5%259b%259b%25e5%2588%25b0%25e6%259c%259f%25e7%25a4%25be%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e8%25b7%259d%25e9%259b%25a2%25e6%258e%25aa%25e6%2596%25bd%25e7%25b6%25ad%25e6%258c%2581%25e4%25b8%258d%25e8%25ae%258a-%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2582%25b2%25e5%25b1%2580%25e4%25b8%258b%25e5%2591%25a8%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e7%2582%25ba%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25b0%258f%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e5%25b9%25bc%25e7%25a8%259a%25e5%259c%2592%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2581%25b7%25e5%2593%25a1%25e9%25a9%2597%25e7%2597%2585%25e6%25af%2592&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0Er9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=b85acd75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%25